**Procfile:**
```
web: uvicorn main:app --host 0.0.0.0 --port $PORT
```

**README.md:**
```
# Eglor AI Buddy

A playful AI buddy for kids, designed to chat with Iweel in a warm and affectionate way! Hosted on Railway.

## Setup Instructions

1. Clone the repository:
   ```sh
   git clone https://github.com/your-username/eglor-ai-buddy.git
   ```

2. Navigate into the project folder:
   ```sh
   cd eglor-ai-buddy
   ```

3. Create a virtual environment:
   ```sh
   python -m venv venv
   source venv/bin/activate  # On Windows use `venv\Scripts\activate`
   ```

4. Install dependencies:
   ```sh
   pip install -r requirements.txt
   ```

5. Set up your `.env` file with your OpenAI API key:
   ```
   OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_api_key_here
   ```

6. Run the FastAPI server:
   ```sh
   uvicorn main:app --reload
   ```

7. Deploy to Railway and connect it with your frontend.
```

**.gitignore:**
```
__pycache__/
venv/
.env
.DS_Store
```

Upload these files to GitHub and your backend will be fully set up! ðŸš€
